# .windsurfrules — Multi-Agent Build System v4.0

> Build PantyHub using agent bundles.
> Read docs/CONTEXT.md first.

## Cascade Execution (one agent per session)

1. Read `docs/agents/schema.md` — execute all phases (Schema Agent)
1. Read `docs/agents/pages.md` — execute all phases (Pages Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/error-handling.md` — execute all phases (Error Handling Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/responsive.md` — execute all phases (Responsive Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-payments.md` — execute all phases (Payments (Stripe) Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-uploads.md` — execute all phases (File Uploads Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-realtime.md` — execute all phases (Realtime Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-search.md` — execute all phases (Full-Text Search Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-notifications.md` — execute all phases (Notifications Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-messaging.md` — execute all phases (Direct Messaging Agent)
2. Read `docs/agents/feature-reviews.md` — execute all phases (Reviews & Ratings Agent)
3. Read `docs/agents/security.md` — execute all phases (Security Agent)
3. Read `docs/agents/devops.md` — execute all phases (DevOps Agent)
4. Read `docs/agents/qa.md` — execute all phases (Quality Assurance Agent)
4. Read `docs/agents/smoke-test.md` — execute all phases (Smoke Test Agent)
5. Read `docs/agents/build-proof.md` — execute all phases (Build Proof Agent)
5. Read `docs/agents/shipgate.md` — execute all phases (ShipGate Agent)

After each agent: `npx tsc --noEmit && npm run build`

